  <summary date="2021-09-20T20:10:53Z" status="Introduced in House">Accurate Data for Defense (ADD) Resiliency Act

This bill requires the Department of Defense to develop and implement a process to ensure it uses analytical tools that are accurate and effective in projecting the costs and performance of energy resilience measures on military installations.</summary>
